  "text": "Targetron® (Sigma) was used for insertional inactivation of pta in HI4320 (Table 4 ). The procedure was modified as described by [CITATION_1] . The mutant ptaWaphA3 was confirmed PCR and sequencing and also using polyclonal Anti-Pta antibody.",
